						<div class="postbody">I managed to do something: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://snowmoons.com/downloads.php?cmd=get_file&amp;id=717">http://snowmoons.com/downloads.php?cmd=get_file&amp;id=717</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br /> zip includes an  executable and an editable game maker 5 file. Screenshot:
<br /> <img src="http://img238.imageshack.us/img238/4161/fightingscreenshot.png" alt="Image" />
<br />By <a href="http://profile.imageshack.us/user/tinytoonboy" class="postlink">tinytoonboy</a> at 2009-03-24
<br />
<br />  You can walk and jump with the arrow keys. By now only a simple punch with key Z. The grid around the characters(representing the tiles) will be removed, I just thought it was ok by now.
<br />
<br /> I think now we can continue discussing the game and change/add things.</div>

